# Developer Portfolio â€” Part 2 (Interactive)

This project implements **Part 2** of the "React Deeper: Build Your Developer Portfolio" assignment.
It includes:
- Controlled contact form with debounced email validation and autosave (localStorage)
- Live preview and toast + confetti on submit
- Feedback wall with rating cards and featured badge
- Projects section with filters, detail toggles, and hover animations
- Theme toggle (Light / Dark / Ocean) persisted in localStorage
- Simulated polling updates displayed in a scrolling ticker
- Small interactive extras: avatar, animations, responsive layout

## Run locally
1. Install dependencies:
   ```bash
   npm install
